com.github.lecogiteur.csvbang.annotation
Annotation Type CsvFooter

@Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Inherited
@Documented
public @interface CsvFooter

Defines options about footer of file

Version:
0.1.0
Author:
Tony EMMA

Optional Element Summary
 String customFooter
          You can define your custom static footer.
 boolean noEndRecordOnLastRecord
          If you want to put (or not) the end record characters on the last record.
 

customFooter

public abstract String customFooter
You can define your custom static footer. By default no custom footer is defined. The footer is writen at the end of file

Returns:
Return a static custom footer
Since:
0.1.0
Default:
"null"

noEndRecordOnLastRecord

public abstract boolean noEndRecordOnLastRecord
If you want to put (or not) the end record characters on the last record. By default false.

Returns:
true if you don't want the end record on the last record
Since:
0.1.0
Default:
false
